        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Savills has been in the real estate business since 1855. They are headquartered in London, UK, along with their vast corporate spread across 700 offices in more than 70 countries situated in the Americas, Europe, Asia Pacific, Africa, and the Middle East. Their real estate services portfolio includes selling and leasing residential and commercial properties, valuation and consultancy, property and facility management, investment advisory, development services, and market research."
        },
        {
          "t": "img",
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/savills-reb6f7dtiyiw5ofu4vsmvdys4xzyvzp2ffgjjasafk.webp",
