    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Data Fragmentation & Inconsistent Reporting"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Savills struggled to establish a cohesive and optimized reporting environment. The primary goal was to aggregate and optimize data from multiple disparate data sources. These data sources comprised Microsoft Dynamics F&O and Salesforce alongside other file-based uploads within Azure Data Lake and SharePoint. This fragmentation of data resulted in:"
        },
        {
          "t": "cta",
          "text": "OVERCOME REAL ESTATE DATA CHALLENGES",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Manual compilation of diverse dietary preferences from numerous sources caused time delays"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Relied on manual efforts for data consolidation, eating up valuable time and hindering operational scalability"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The varying data extraction methods led to reporting inconsistencies and discrepancies"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The reports lacked operational insights, hindering strategic initiatives and decision-making"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The lack of real-time reporting missed out on taking critical business decisions on-spot for the efficient performance"
        }
      ],
      "headings": [
