    {
      "items": [
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Real Estate Data Consolidation and Reporting Using Microsoft Fabric"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 collaborated with Savills to transform their reporting landscape. We designed and implemented Microsoft Fabric, which produced a scalable reporting solution. We took two approaches, optimizing their current reporting assets and constructing a complete 360° reporting platform. The main aspects of the solution were:"
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Strategic Optimization of Existing Reports"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "We deeply analyzed Savills’ existing reporting infrastructure to highlight bottlenecks and refine reporting logic for maximized performance and data accuracy."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Microsoft Fabric as the Core Analytics Platform"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "We established a cloud-native data analytics platform. It served as the main pillar system for data ingestion, transformation, and analysis."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Medallion Architecture Implementation"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "Implemented Medallion Architecture within MS Fabric, which consisted of Fabric Lakehouses to ingest raw data from disparate sources, then cleaning this raw data using Fabric Pipelines and Notebooks."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Automated Data Pipelines"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The data pipelines within MS Fabric utilizes ETL process in ingesting data timely and efficiently along with effortless movement between Medallion layers."
        },
        {
          "t": "h",
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Data Unification & Consolidation"
        },
        {
          "t": "p",
          "text": "The meticulous schema design and transformation logic with Fabric Notebooks, we managed to unify the data, creating a central data repository and eliminating silos for holistic business performance analysis."
        },
        {
          "t": "cta",
          "text": "EXPLORE OUR REAL ESTATE DATA SOLUTIONS",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
